title: Deep Sea Python
subTitle: Fisherman Chen Yue and photographer Zhong Ming must set aside their differences after being attacked by a sea creature in the middle of the ocean.

title: Gangster
subTitle: Simran, who relocates to Seoul, is distraught when Daya, a gangster, re-enters her life. She has to make a choice between him and her lover Akash, who is a singer at an Indian restaurant.

subTitle: Aditya, Joe, Kedar and Rob form a rock band but break up when they fail to succeed. They lead regular lives until deciding to reunite and take another shot at fulfilling their dreams.

title: 50 Days of Love
subTitle: A gynaecologist reluctantly gets married to a simple woman. However, things take a drastic turn when they both start getting to know each other and uncover the lies they fed one another.

title: Darlings
subTitle: Badru desperately wishes her abusive husband mends his ill-treatment of her. However, when her situation worsens, Badru takes matters into her own hands.

title: Aitraaz
subTitle: When a company chairman's trophy wife stirs up a storm in a happily married employee's life, the tumultuous winds drag all of them into an intense courtroom showdown.

title: Aranmanai 4
subTitle: Suspicious about his sister's death, Saravanan, a lawyer, tries to solve the mystery behind it, only to discover a mysteriously dark force at play.

title: Baaghi
subTitle: Raja loves Rani, but she commits suicide after falling prey to Manmohan, who wants her at any cost. A devastated Raja turns to the world of crime and becomes a professional killer.

title: Sooryavanshi
subTitle: With the looming threat of a terrorist attack on Mumbai, ATS chief Sooryavanshi embarks on a mission to hunt for 600 kgs of missing RDX and the conspiring perpetrators.

title: Spyder
subTitle: Shiva, an intelligence officer, develops a phone software that helps him track those in need of help. He sets out to save the people of Hyderabad when he realises that a serial killer is on the loose.

title: Farrey
subTitle: Brought up in an orphanage, child prodigy Niyati gets admitted into a prestigious school. Soon, surrounded by money, she gets engulfed in a cheating racket.

subTitle: Karan, an aimless young man, joins the Indian Army on a whim but backs out when he finds a soldier's life to be difficult. When this creates conflict with his girlfriend, he rejoins to make her proud.

subTitle: The thirst for power drives a wealthy family to become rivals in a risky heist. As a consequence, they face betrayal and danger along the way.

subTitle: Jaya marries Keshav but is disappointed to learn that there is no toilet in his house. As a result, he tries to pacify her with temporary arrangements.

subTitle: An army intelligence officer arrives in Mumbai to spend the holiday with his family. However, he must switch back to work mode after a bomb rips through the heart of the city.

subTitle: A police officer and soldier team up and decide to end the cybercriminals that pose a threat to the safety of people on the Internet.

title: Ajab Gazabb Love
subTitle: Rajveer, a rich man, falls in love with Madhuri. However, he soon realises that she detests affluent people and in order to win her heart, he, along with his family, pretends to be poor.

title: Manmarziyaan
subTitle: A young, free-spirited woman is torn between two very different men and must decide who to marry. One is an immature, part-time DJ, while the other is a mature and responsible banker.

subTitle: Four young women navigate love, family, and careers while supporting one another. The childhood friends are brought together for Kalindi's wedding and are forced to untangle their lives.

title: Double Dhamaal
subTitle: Four idlers make elaborate plans to earn money by investing in buildings but are conned by Kabir, who leaves them unemployed and penniless. Soon, they are on the prowl to avenge their humiliation.

title: Dabangg 2
subTitle: Inspector Chulbul Pandey oversees the operations of the local police station in Kanpur. However, things take a turn when he kills the brother of a local politician.

title: Raksha Bandhan
subTitle: Embracing his role as the provider, Lala Kedarnath puts personal romantic interests on the back burner until his quirky sisters can be married off into loving families.

title: Maayon
subTitle: An archaeological team arrives at a historical temple to learn about its secrets. Meanwhile, a group of idol smugglers plan to steal the hidden treasure inside the temple.

title: Gumnaam
subTitle: An aspiring director reluctantly becomes a police officer. Soon after, he starts investigating a serial murder case wherein the killer targets teenage girls.

title: Kho Gaye Hum Kahan
subTitle: Three friends in their twenties, Imaad, Ahana, and Neil, try to figure out life in an ever changing digital era. So, through love and heartbreak, they find support in each other.

title: Commando - A One Man Army
subTitle: Caught in the diplomatic crossfire between India and China, Captain Karan Dogra fights a harrowing battle for survival and makes a new enemy by rescuing a damsel in distress.
